      <title>加州进一步为奴隶制的危害道歉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-21/california-moves-closer-to-apologizing-for-the-harms-of-slavery</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加州立法者使该州距离成为美国第一个为奴隶制危害道歉的州又近了一步，尽管这种做法在该州从来不合法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-21/california-moves-closer-to-apologizing-for-the-harms-of-slavery</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 18:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊利诺伊州拟将体育博彩税提高至 527 亿美元预算</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-21/illinois-eyes-sports-betting-tax-hike-for-52-7-billion-budget</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊利诺伊州州长 J.B. Pritzker 提议从 7 月开始的年度预算为 527 亿美元，提高体育博彩税并扩大企业税收减免上限。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-21/illinois-eyes-sports-betting-tax-hike-for-52-7-billion-budget</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 18:22:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度延长蒸谷米出口税以控制价格</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-21/india-extends-parboiled-rice-export-tax-to-control-prices</link>
      <description><![CDATA[全球最大的大米出口国印度延长了对预煮品种的出口征税，以防止大选前国内价格上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-21/india-extends-parboiled-rice-export-tax-to-control-prices</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 18:18:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟准备向波兰提供因法治冲突而受阻的援助</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-21/eu-poised-to-release-polish-funds-blocked-in-rule-of-law-clash</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟最早将于下周向波兰发放 63 亿欧元（合 68 亿美元）的疫情后援助，以对新政府修复与布鲁塞尔关系的能力投下重大信任票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-21/eu-poised-to-release-polish-funds-blocked-in-rule-of-law-clash</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 18:11:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>罗马尼亚最高政党就欧盟选举政治联盟达成一致</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-21/romanian-top-parties-agree-on-political-alliance-for-eu-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[罗马尼亚两个执政党同意组建政治联盟，并在今年的几轮选举中选出联合候选人，以限制极端民族主义政党的崛起。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-21/romanian-top-parties-agree-on-political-alliance-for-eu-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 17:57:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>投票前南非的慷慨预算对非国大来说是个好消息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-21/south-africa-s-houdini-budget-gives-anc-leeway-before-crux-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[距离选举还有三个月，南非财政部长提交了一份预算，其中规定了吸引选票的支出增加和遏制债务的计划，这让投资者欢呼雀跃。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-21/south-africa-s-houdini-budget-gives-anc-leeway-before-crux-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 17:46:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>索齐获胜后，纽约民主党的目标是在汉普顿获胜</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-21/cnn-analyst-buoyed-by-suozzi-plans-run-in-hamptons-for-ny-seat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国有线电视新闻网(CNN)政治分析师约翰·阿夫隆(John Avlon)表示，汤姆·索齐(Tom Suozzi)上周在乔治·桑托斯(George Santos)空出的众议院席位特别选举中取得决定性胜利，这表明民主党如何能够在长岛获胜。而他也想亲自证明这一点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-21/cnn-analyst-buoyed-by-suozzi-plans-run-in-hamptons-for-ny-seat</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 17:25:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿拉巴马大学在胚胎裁决后暂停治疗</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-21/university-of-alabama-pauses-ivf-treatment-after-state-s-ruling</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿拉巴马大学伯明翰分校已暂停试管受精治疗，因为它正在审查该州最高法院的一项裁决，该裁决确定冷冻胚胎应被视为儿童。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-21/university-of-alabama-pauses-ivf-treatment-after-state-s-ruling</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 16:19:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国称前联邦调查局线人与俄罗斯情报部门有联系</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-21/us-says-former-fbi-informant-had-ties-to-russian-intelligence</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国检察官在一份法庭文件中写道，一名线人被控就亨特·拜登及其父亲与乌克兰能源公司布里斯马控股公司的关系向联邦调查局撒谎，该线人与俄罗斯情报人员有多次接触。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-21/us-says-former-fbi-informant-had-ties-to-russian-intelligence</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 16:14:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苏纳克团队与邮局发生口角意味着丑闻不会消失</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-21/sunak-team-s-war-of-words-on-post-office-scandal-spurs-backlash</link>
      <description><![CDATA[距离英国大选还有几个月，在民意调查中落后的英国首相里希·苏纳克迫切希望摆脱被称为英国法律史上最大丑闻的事实：数千名店主被错误地指控从他们经营的邮局特许经营权中盗窃。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-21/sunak-team-s-war-of-words-on-post-office-scandal-spurs-backlash</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 14:41:46 GMT</pubDate>
